rows.label: tlk42100149_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Acting agent of Nilny is thick as
two planks! We letting huge business
opportunity get away!

rows.label: tlk42100149_03_msg0002
rows.name:
We told to strictly sell at reasonable
price for customers! What he thinking?!
That not the merchant way!

rows.label: tlk42100149_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Shortage of goods mean chance for
huge profit! This point where we hike
prices up to monumental level!

rows.label: tlk42100149_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Chamomo miss days of Chairman Bahn
and Don. Back then, we allowed to use
any means possible to reap profit...

rows.label: tlk42100149_03_msg0005
rows.name:
O-of course, Chamomo never dream of
using illegal methods! Career would be
over if caught!

rows.label: tlk42100149_03_msg0006
rows.name:
M-merchants all about trust and
understanding! Is important to
crack down on crime!
